            <title>[SOLR-5438] DebugComponent throws NPE when used with grouping</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-5438</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;To Reproduce: &lt;br/&gt;
